Package: boundary
Version: 0.0.1
Title: Confidence Interval Estimation at y=0 for Linear Regression Models
Authors@R: c(
  person("Ray", "Zhu", email = "rayzhuca@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Norm", "Matloff", email = "matloff@cs.ucdavis.edu", 
         role = c("aut"), 
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9179-6785")))
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    nloptr,
    plotly
Imports: stats
Description: This package implements statistical methods for estimating confidence intervals of the 
    at y=0 in linear regression models. Provides both delta method and Lagrange multiplier approaches.
    Also includes utilities for 3D visualization of results.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/matloff/boundary
BugReports: https://github.com/matloff/boundary/issues